<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>周easy - 輕鬆學程式</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-yellow: #FFD93D;
            --secondary-blue: #6BCB77;
            --accent-blue: #4D96FF;
            --bg-color: #F9F9F9;
            --text-dark: #2B2B2B;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif, "Microsoft JhengHei";
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            background-color: var(--primary-yellow);
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #FF6B6B;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px white;
        }

        p.subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .nav-card {
            background: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border: 3px solid transparent;
        }

        .nav-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-color: var(--primary-yellow);
        }

        /* 不同的色塊裝飾 */
        .c-lang { border-bottom: 8px solid #A8B9CC; }
        .cpp-lang { border-bottom: 8px solid #00599C; }
        .py-lang { border-bottom: 8px solid #3776AB; }
        .go-lang { border-bottom: 8px solid #00ADD8; }

        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>周easy 🚀</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">寫程式沒那麼難，我們輕鬆點學！</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <a href="#c" class="nav-card c-lang">C 語言</a>
        <a href="#cpp" class="nav-card cpp-lang">C++ 進階</a>
        <a href="#python" class="nav-card py-lang">Python 腳本</a>
        <a href="#go" class="nav-card go-lang">Go 併發</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 周easy 教學網頁 - 讓學習變簡單
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
